nabla(∇) uses two licenses for two different kinds of material in this
repository, because source code and educational content have different
licensing needs (see LICENSES.md for the exact directory boundaries).

  * Source code (components, libraries, build scripts) is licensed
    under the GNU General Public License v3.0 or later.
    See LICENSE-CODE for the full text.

  * MDX lesson content, prose, and original diagrams/figures are
    licensed under Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0
    International (CC BY-SA 4.0).
    See LICENSE-CONTENT for the full text.

Third-party assets, fonts, and dependencies retain their own licenses;
see LICENSES.md for details.

This file is a summary for convenience. In case of any conflict, the
full license texts in LICENSE-CODE and LICENSE-CONTENT govern.
